   "text": "• mu  drift — small; folded into fair value\n• sigma dW  diffusion = news-driven belief drift (belief-vol)\n• J dN  jumps = resolution / dispute / shock\n\nEstimate sigma, lambda+cost, fair X  →  that's the whole quant.",
