   "text": "No clean closed form for jump-diffusion MM (directional jumps) - research-grade. The jump handling is a\nPRINCIPLED HEURISTIC, empirically tuned, NOT a theorem. Diffusion A-S is the rigorous base.  Quote: bid=r-d/2, ask=r+d/2.",
