   "fontSize": 11,
   "fontFamily": 2,
   "text": "• MODEL RISK now dominant — bad sigma/lambda → SYSTEMATICALLY wrong (worse than naive-wrong). edge is conditional on calibration.\n• estimation weakest EXACTLY where it matters — thin, contested, long-tail markets have the least clean data.\n• regime change — params fit in calm periods misfire in election weeks; a short EWMA lags turns.\n• the directional jump can't be fully dodged — exit-on-risk cuts adverse-selection/haircut exposure, never to zero.",
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "• MODEL RISK now dominant — bad sigma/lambda → SYSTEMATICALLY wrong (worse than naive-wrong). edge is conditional on calibration.\n• estimation weakest EXACTLY where it matters — thin, contested, long-tail markets have the least clean data.\n• regime change — params fit in calm periods misfire in election weeks; a short EWMA lags turns.\n• the directional jump can't be fully dodged — exit-on-risk cuts adverse-selection/haircut exposure, never to zero.",
   "lineHeight": 1.25,
   "baseline": 9
  },
