   "fontSize": 10,
   "fontFamily": 2,
   "text": "PRICING / AVELLANEDA-STOIKOV\n• Avellaneda-Stoikov - the classic formula for bid/ask\n   given inventory, vol, time (a quote thermostat)\n• s - mid price (current fair middle)\n• r - reservation price = YOUR fair value after inventory;\n   long -> r drops -> quote lower to sell down\n• q - inventory: shares held (+long / -short)\n• gamma - risk aversion: how much you hate risk\n   (high=wider spread, faster shedding)\n• (T-t) - time left to resolution; ->0 at the buzzer\n• delta (d) - the spread (gap bid<->ask); wider=more\n   cushion, fewer fills\n• k - liquidity: how fast fills dry up away from mid (high\n   k=thin)\n• kappa - jump-premium weight: extra spread for jump risk\n   (NOT the same as k)\n• inventory skew - shift both quotes to lean against your\n   inventory",
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "PRICING / AVELLANEDA-STOIKOV\n• Avellaneda-Stoikov - the classic formula for bid/ask\n   given inventory, vol, time (a quote thermostat)\n• s - mid price (current fair middle)\n• r - reservation price = YOUR fair value after inventory;\n   long -> r drops -> quote lower to sell down\n• q - inventory: shares held (+long / -short)\n• gamma - risk aversion: how much you hate risk\n   (high=wider spread, faster shedding)\n• (T-t) - time left to resolution; ->0 at the buzzer\n• delta (d) - the spread (gap bid<->ask); wider=more\n   cushion, fewer fills\n• k - liquidity: how fast fills dry up away from mid (high\n   k=thin)\n• kappa - jump-premium weight: extra spread for jump risk\n   (NOT the same as k)\n• inventory skew - shift both quotes to lean against your\n   inventory",
   "lineHeight": 1.25,
   "baseline": 20
  },
  {
   "type": "text",
   "version": 1,
   "versionNonce": 900000183,
   "isDeleted": false,
   "id": "glossK_col4",
   "fillStyle": "solid",
   "strokeWidth": 2,
   "strokeStyle": "solid",
   "roughness": 0,
   "opacity": 100,
   "angle": 0,
