   "roundness": null,
   "boundElements": [],
   "updated": 1735000000001,
   "link": null,
   "locked": false,
   "fontSize": 10,
   "fontFamily": 2,
   "text": "EXECUTION, VALIDATION & ON-CHAIN\n• exit-on-risk - on proposal/lambda-spike, cancel & reduce\n   before danger (now reward-aware)\n• adverse selection - getting picked off: your stale order\n   trades right before bad news\n• CLOB - Central Limit Order Book = the exchange’s resting\n   buy/sell list\n• maker / taker - maker posts a resting order (rewards, no\n   fee); taker crosses to fill now (pays fee)\n• post-only - order that refuses to be a taker (guarantees\n   maker status)\n• rewards / rebates - daily payout for tight two-sided\n   orders / a share of taker fees\n• ablation - turn a part OFF to measure its worth (A/B\n   test the lambda term)\n• P&L - profit and loss\n• UMA OOv2 / DVM - oracle that decides outcomes; DVM =\n   token-holder vote settling disputes\n• conditionId/questionId - on-chain IDs joining a\n   Polymarket market to its UMA question\n• reconciliation - check indexed outcome == on-chain\n   payout",
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "EXECUTION, VALIDATION & ON-CHAIN\n• exit-on-risk - on proposal/lambda-spike, cancel & reduce\n   before danger (now reward-aware)\n• adverse selection - getting picked off: your stale order\n   trades right before bad news\n• CLOB - Central Limit Order Book = the exchange’s resting\n   buy/sell list\n• maker / taker - maker posts a resting order (rewards, no\n   fee); taker crosses to fill now (pays fee)\n• post-only - order that refuses to be a taker (guarantees\n   maker status)\n• rewards / rebates - daily payout for tight two-sided\n   orders / a share of taker fees\n• ablation - turn a part OFF to measure its worth (A/B\n   test the lambda term)\n• P&L - profit and loss\n• UMA OOv2 / DVM - oracle that decides outcomes; DVM =\n   token-holder vote settling disputes\n• conditionId/questionId - on-chain IDs joining a\n   Polymarket market to its UMA question\n• reconciliation - check indexed outcome == on-chain\n   payout",
   "lineHeight": 1.25,
   "baseline": 20
  },
