   "text": "① HF DATASET — DuckDB over hf://   (DATA_SOURCE=hf, default)\nmoose-code/polymarket-onchain-v1 · 2.74B records · 1.17B fills · 2022–2026 (74% in 2026)\n992,485 resolved conditions · no download (query in place)\n• order_filled → σ / fair-value tape (single-axis, min(tokenId))\n• condition.payoutNumerators → recon truth + λ base-rate denominators\n• market_data → tokenId↔conditionId map + keyword category",
