   "text": "② DISPUTE LABELS — the one thing HF lacks\ndata/disputes.py: OOv2 DisputePrice via KEYLESS RPC (no Docker)\n→ conditionId = keccak256(adapter‖keccak(ancillary)‖2) → join HF\nV2 + Legacy: 723/723 joined (100%)\nNegRisk: not keccak-derivable → recovered via data/negrisk_map.py\n   (NegRiskOperator QuestionPrepared → tradeable cid) → 943/943 (100%)\nscoped local Envio indexer = the net-new OOv2 lifecycle (Docker optional)",
