   "text": "⋈ JOIN on conditionId (V2/Legacy 723/723 · NegRisk 943/943 via negrisk_map = 100%)    ·    recon GATE: indexed finalOutcome == HF payoutNumerators (pass_rate 1.0 eligible; NegRisk → no_ground_truth)",
