   "link": null,
   "locked": false,
   "fontSize": 10,
   "fontFamily": 2,
   "text": "DATA SOURCES & TOOLS\n• HF dataset (HuggingFace) — a free public download of\n   Polymarket’s whole on-chain history (2.74B records, 1.17B\n   fills) — every trade + outcome\n• DuckDB — an in-process SQL engine (\"SQLite for analytics\")\n   that scans big files fast; queries the dataset in place\n• parquet / hf:// — parquet = compressed columnar files;\n   hf:// = read them straight from HuggingFace\n• DATA_SOURCE (hf | graphql) — \"hf\" = public dataset +\n   keyless-RPC disputes (default, no Docker); \"graphql\" =\n   your own indexer\n• keyless RPC (tenderly) — a public Polygon node needing no\n   API key; how disputes are pulled without running an\n   indexer\n• materialize slice / cache — copy just the markets you need\n   to local parquet once, so re-runs are instant\n• companion dataset — the extracted dispute labels re-\n   published as polymarket-oov2-disputes-v1\n   (data/export_disputes.py)",
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "DATA SOURCES & TOOLS\n• HF dataset (HuggingFace) — a free public download of\n   Polymarket’s whole on-chain history (2.74B records, 1.17B\n   fills) — every trade + outcome\n• DuckDB — an in-process SQL engine (\"SQLite for analytics\")\n   that scans big files fast; queries the dataset in place\n• parquet / hf:// — parquet = compressed columnar files;\n   hf:// = read them straight from HuggingFace\n• DATA_SOURCE (hf | graphql) — \"hf\" = public dataset +\n   keyless-RPC disputes (default, no Docker); \"graphql\" =\n   your own indexer\n• keyless RPC (tenderly) — a public Polygon node needing no\n   API key; how disputes are pulled without running an\n   indexer\n• materialize slice / cache — copy just the markets you need\n   to local parquet once, so re-runs are instant\n• companion dataset — the extracted dispute labels re-\n   published as polymarket-oov2-disputes-v1\n   (data/export_disputes.py)",
   "lineHeight": 1.25,
   "baseline": 20
  },
