   "fontSize": 10,
   "fontFamily": 2,
   "text": "JOINING & NORMALIZING\n• conditionId — the shared market id; the KEY matching HF\n   fills/outcomes to dispute labels\n• single-axis (min tokenId) — a market has YES+NO tokens;\n   pick one canonical side (other = 1−price)\n• payoutNumerators — the on-chain result vector ([1,0]=YES,\n   [0,1]=NO); recon’s ground truth\n• category (keyword) — market bucket\n   (crypto/sports/politics…) guessed from the title/slug\n• NegRisk map (tradeable cid) — NegRisk markets trade under\n   a different conditionId (oracle = NegRiskAdapter),\n   recovered from QuestionPrepared → 132,004 mapped, 100% in\n   HF\n• phantom conditionId — a fake id the indexer computed for\n   NegRisk that exists nowhere on-chain; caused the earlier\n   \"0% joinable\" bug\n• market_data / condition — HF tables: market_data =\n   token↔condition map; condition = resolved outcomes",
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "JOINING & NORMALIZING\n• conditionId — the shared market id; the KEY matching HF\n   fills/outcomes to dispute labels\n• single-axis (min tokenId) — a market has YES+NO tokens;\n   pick one canonical side (other = 1−price)\n• payoutNumerators — the on-chain result vector ([1,0]=YES,\n   [0,1]=NO); recon’s ground truth\n• category (keyword) — market bucket\n   (crypto/sports/politics…) guessed from the title/slug\n• NegRisk map (tradeable cid) — NegRisk markets trade under\n   a different conditionId (oracle = NegRiskAdapter),\n   recovered from QuestionPrepared → 132,004 mapped, 100% in\n   HF\n• phantom conditionId — a fake id the indexer computed for\n   NegRisk that exists nowhere on-chain; caused the earlier\n   \"0% joinable\" bug\n• market_data / condition — HF tables: market_data =\n   token↔condition map; condition = resolved outcomes",
